est, the pixie will pick the lock for me. Very cool.<br><br>The monk started with a feat called Cleave. Cleave gives you an automatic free attack on an adjacent mob if your last hit killed the mob you were fighting. In other words, you punch Goblin A and kill it. Then you get a free attack on Goblin B, which was standing next to Goblin A. There's a ton more stuff too, but I don't feel like typing all day.<br><br> <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4758>Klair</a><br><a href=http://www.the-kindred.org>The Kindred</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/ufantasmvi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fantasm VI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><font color=#33cc33>Drinalite</font></span><br>  Posts: 125<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/21/02 11:25:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3283.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: NWN is worth it</span><hr size=1> Klairen, we should play sometime.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/udoofyrainbowfloatar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Doofy Rainbowfloatar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>No Life</span><br>  Posts: 1416<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/23/02 10:23:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3283.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ...</span><hr size=1> I'm really enjoying Nwn...<br><br><br>Good graphics, great sound...good plot. The game is also challenging, but very unpredictable.<br><br>I can go up against something that's overpowering, and tear the shit out of it in a matter of seconds, or I can go up to something &quot;